{"tid":1493592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 觀塘vs機場","createTime":"2019-08-21T09:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T18:16:20.000Z","uid":120308,"like":57,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b74898efa358857d2530d8e3955dcfb4be6cd1ce","tid":1493592,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"[頂 頭先開錯台]<br />\n我真係唸唔到點解要繼續地區遊行，<br />\n本來唸住遍地開花先地區遊行，而家都冇咩地方未開<br />\n差唔多到到都有蛋食，<br />\n<br />\n地區遊行風險高，易送頭，又多鬼<br />\n觀塘仲要行工廠區，星期6影都唔多隻<br />\n相反機場係香港心臟，你一塞<br />\n睇下政府幾大反應，又出禁制令又大大聲屌哂鬼<br />\n地區遊行反而只係食放題，政府都唔多理你<br />\n<br />\n我8.24就揀清明上河圖啦<br />\n<br />\n觀塘撚唔該入來 用文明說服我! <br />\n唔好話一早排左隊，你估餐廳食飯，先到先得呀<br />\n而家做野要有效先得架，be water 個心態都要be water<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀塘"},{"pid":"bba81eaaf81df4aeed749cc1605dddde10bb9386","tid":1493592,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d96450ff6f1421f18c64761ac6974a8e3d355164","tid":1493592,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8724af011993a0d44f8d152a9ccb5457cee90d8","tid":1493592,"uid":92340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"即係以後都唔使遊行lu~係咪咁既意思？"},{"pid":"7529c307313642af69b4e4ab532f5ec4b8e00ecc","tid":1493592,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36e2fe0303182f8d2dcac0fd4af83aecdd74247","tid":1493592,"uid":120308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8724af011993a0d44f8d152a9ccb5457cee90d8","tid":1493592,"uid":92340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"即係以後都唔使遊行lu~係咪咁既意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"遊行主要用來哂馬，好似818咁"},{"pid":"1e60a85bcabc3f6d473e06c8fa8c14084eb943e7